RelatedSentence: A Monday morning search warrant executed by the Russell County Sheriff 's Office and the Kansas Bureau of Investigation in Dorrance resulted in the arrest of a woman after methamphetamine was found in her residence .
According to a press release from the Sheriff 's Office , at 9:47 AM Monday , officers from the Sheriff 's Office and KBI executed a search warrant at 916 North Lincoln Ave in Dorrance .
The Russell Police Department was called over to look at the items .
The PD executed a separate search warrant at the same location and seized several items .
